{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-12-transaction/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1 id=\"transaction\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#transaction\" aria-label=\"transaction permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>transaction</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>논리적인 작업 단위</li>\n<li>여러 SQL 문을 단일 작업으로 묶은 것</li>\n<li>트랜잭션의 SQL 문들은 일부만 성공하여 DB에 반영되지 않는다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"트랜잭션-사용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"트랜잭션 사용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>트랜잭션 사용 방법</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>이체 과정을 트랜잭션으로 묶어서 처리</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"35820367148694210000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`> BEGIN TRANSACTION; -- 이후 명령어들을 하나의 트랜잭션으로 묶음\r\n\r\n> UPDATE accounts SET balance = balance - 100 WHERE account_id = 1;\r\n> UPDATE accounts SET balance = balance + 100 WHERE account_id = 2;\r\n\r\n> COMMIT; -- 지금까지 작업한 내용을 DB에 용구적으로 저장, 트랜잭션 종료`, `35820367148694210000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRANSACTION</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 이후 명령어들을 하나의 트랜잭션으로 묶음</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> accounts <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> account_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> accounts <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> account_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">COMMIT</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 지금까지 작업한 내용을 DB에 용구적으로 저장, 트랜잭션 종료</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"rollback\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rollback\" aria-label=\"rollback permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ROLLBACK</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션 중 발생한 오류로 인해 트랜잭션 취소</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"4937181502352783000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`> START TRANSACTION;\r\n\r\n> UPDATE accounts SET balance = balance - 100 WHERE account_id = 1;\r\n\r\n> SELECT * FROM accounts; -- 1번 계좌의 잔액이 100 감소한 것을 확인\r\n\r\n> ROLLBACK; -- 트랜잭션 취소\r\n\r\n> SELECT * FROM accounts; -- 처음 상태로 돌아감`, `4937181502352783000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">START</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRANSACTION</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> accounts <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> balance <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> account_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> accounts<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 1번 계좌의 잔액이 100 감소한 것을 확인</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ROLLBACK</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 트랜잭션 취소</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> accounts<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 처음 상태로 돌아감</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"autocommit\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#autocommit\" aria-label=\"autocommit permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AUTOCOMMIT</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>SQL문이 성공적으로 실행되면 자동으로 <code class=\"language-text\">COMMIT</code></li>\n<li>실행 중 문제가 있다면 자동으로 <code class=\"language-text\">ROLLBACK</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">MYSQL</code>에서는 기본적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">AUTOCOMMIT</code>이 켜져있음</li>\n<li>단일 SQL문이 성공에서 DB 반영되는 이유는 사실 <code class=\"language-text\">AUTOCOMMIT</code>이 켜져있기 때문</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">START TRANSACTION</code> 명령어는 트랜잭션 시작과 동시에 <code class=\"language-text\">AUTOCOMMIT</code>을 끄는 역할을 함</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">COMMIT</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">ROLLBACK</code> 명령어는 <code class=\"language-text\">AUTOCOMMIT</code>을 켜는 역할을 함</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"63079142124341290000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`> SET AUTOCOMMIT = 0; -- AUTOCOMMIT 끄기\r\n\r\n> DELETE FROM accounts WHERE account_id = 1; -- 1번 계좌 삭제\r\n\r\n> SELECT * FROM accounts; -- 1번 계좌 삭제된 것을 확인\r\n\r\n> ROLLBACK; -- 트랜잭션 취소\r\n\r\n> SELECT * FROM accounts; -- 처음 상태로 돌아감`, `63079142124341290000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> AUTOCOMMIT <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- AUTOCOMMIT 끄기</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> accounts <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> account_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 1번 계좌 삭제</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> accounts<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 1번 계좌 삭제된 것을 확인</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ROLLBACK</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 트랜잭션 취소</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> accounts<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 처음 상태로 돌아감</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"acid\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#acid\" aria-label=\"acid permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ACID</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션이 가져야할 특성</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"atomicity\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#atomicity\" aria-label=\"atomicity permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Atomicity</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션은 모두 성공하거나 모두 실패해야 함</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ROLLBACK</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">COMMIT</code> 명령어를 통해 <code class=\"language-text\">ALL or NOTHING</code> 원칙을 지킴</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"consistency\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#consistency\" aria-label=\"consistency permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Consistency</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code>가 깨지는 예시 : 계좌 DB에 음수가 될 수 없는데 0원의 계좌에 10만원을 출금하는 경우 -10만원이 됨 => <code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code>가 깨짐</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d5794c47-a9ff-44ce-94a5-19d9bdc7e0be\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션은 DB를 <code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code> 상태에서 또 다른 <code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code> 상태로 변경해야 함(일관성 유지)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code>이 위반 되었다면 <code class=\"language-text\">ROLLBACK</code> 해야함</li>\n<li>DBMS는 <code class=\"language-text\">COMMIT</code> 전에 <code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code> 상태를 확인하고 공지</li>\n<li>개발자는 로직이 <code class=\"language-text\">consistent</code> 상태를 유지하도록 작성하는지 확인, 개발</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"isolation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#isolation\" aria-label=\"isolation permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Isolation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 트랜잭션이 동시에 실행되어도 혼자 실행되는 것처럼 동작해야 함</li>\n<li>다음과 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">H</code>의 계좌에 트랜잭션이 겹치면 문제가 생김(<code class=\"language-text\">lost update</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a17b19ed-57e8-469a-b4e2-e4edd56bd2a4\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>높은 수준의 격리는 성능이 떨어짐</li>\n<li>DBMS는 여러 종류의 <code class=\"language-text\">isolation level</code>을 제공</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"durability\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#durability\" aria-label=\"durability permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Durability</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>트랜잭션이 <code class=\"language-text\">COMMIT</code>되면 영구적으로 반영되어야 함</li>\n<li>영구적이란 DB system에 문제가 생겨도 데이터가 유실되지 않아야 함 => 하드디스크에 저장되어야 함</li>\n<li>DBMS에서 기본적으로 보장</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"트랜잭션에서-개발자가-고려해야-할-점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A0%A4%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%A0-%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"트랜잭션에서 개발자가 고려해야 할 점 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>트랜잭션에서 개발자가 고려해야 할 점</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>ACID 속성을 기반으로 트랜잭션을 어떻게 정의해서 사용할지 결정</li>\n<li>ACID 속성을 DBMS가 모두 해결해주는 것은 아님, 개발자가 챙겨줘야 함</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#transaction\">transaction</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">트랜잭션 사용 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#rollback\">ROLLBACK</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#autocommit\">AUTOCOMMIT</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#acid\">ACID</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#atomicity\">Atomicity</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#consistency\">Consistency</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#isolation\">Isolation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#durability\">Durability</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A0%A4%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%A0-%EC%A0%90\">트랜잭션에서 개발자가 고려해야 할 점</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"transaction","date":"2025년 01월 12일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-12-transaction/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-11-trigger/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"trigger","date":"2025-01-11 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-13-동시성-제어(serializability)/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"동시성 제어(serializability)","date":"2025-01-13 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}